I agree that a lot of hentai and porn tropes in general are pretty fucked up, and you can question preferences, but your argument seems to boil down to "NTR isn't that bad compared to other things". Maybe so, from an ethical standpoint, but 1. that doesn't make it in itself ethical or okay and 2. there is such a thing as embarrassment by proxy. This is the main issue people have with NTR. It's the same feeling you can get when watching a cringe comedy: a feeling of awkwardness, embarrassment, and anxiety. While clearly there are people who like this it's no surprise that it's a niche taste and that many people don't like it. People generally dislike feeling awkward or embarrassed. And that's fine.
